              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": ". Having read this a couple of times, as far as I can see, it‚Äôs just taking a lot of words to say ‚ÄúAI exists, dunno how we‚Äôll use it, but we‚Äôre playing with it.‚Äù",
                "type": "text",
